               MOVE    ZERO                TO  WRK-DD
               PERFORM VARYING     IDX-D   FROM    1   BY   1
                       UNTIL       IDX-D   >   31
                   IF          ACCT-DAY(1 IDX-D)   >   ZERO
                       MOVE    IDX-D               TO  WRK-DD
                       PERFORM 230-MAIN-SRY-SEC
                   END-IF
               END-PERFORM
